The held-out fold is the half of episodes with the larger seeds within each
environment; coverage is averaged over those held-out traces. Mean reward
is reported with a 95\% percentile-bootstrap confidence interval
($n_{\text{resamples}} = 1000$, deterministic RNG seed for reproducibility).

