\subsection{What this audit does \emph{not} measure}

This is an offline, single-turn capability audit: the model receives a
prompt, returns a structured prediction, and the environment scores it.
The audit therefore says nothing about multi-turn tool use, planning,
training-data leakage, or robustness to adversarial inputs. It also does
not establish causal claims about how to \emph{improve} the model — only
how it currently performs on this fixed evaluation regime.

